Calculate z-scores

Source: R/moments.R
z.scores.Rd

Calculate z-scores

Usage

z.scores(x, ..., na.rm = FALSE)

Arguments

x

a numeric vector of length +2L

...

additional arguments to be passed to function

na.rm

option to remove or keep NAs, set to FALSE by default.

Value

a numeric vector of length 1

Examples

s <- rnorm(30,1,1.4)
z.scores(s)
#>  [1]  0.52061671 -0.30440241 -0.08197321 -0.68957967  1.87283299  0.34404823
